headline: American Electric's Q2 Earnings Beat Estimates, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: AEP posts an 11.7% Q2 earnings beat and 11.1% revenue growth, driven by strong performance across all core segments.

headline: Entergy's Q2 Earnings Improve Y/Y, Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: ETR posts strong Q2 results with earnings up 9.4% and revenue rising 12.7% year over year, beating the consensus estimate.
